query: Find won amount and QTD by year and quarter
sql:
SELECT
    SUM(m.won_amount) AS won_amount, SUM(q.qtd_amount) AS qtd, m.year, m.quarter
FROM cisco_stage_app.metrics AS m
    INNER
    JOIN cisco_stage_app.qtd_commit_upside AS q
    ON m.year = q.year
    AND m.quarter = q.quarter
GROUP BY m.year, m.quarter
